<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1878-03-06T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1878-03-06T00:00:00-05:00" n="511" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d511">
                        <head>No. 506.<lb/><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Maynard</persName> to Mr. <persName type="to">Evarts</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Cipher telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Constantinople</hi> (<hi rend="smallcaps">Pera</hi>)</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1878-03-06"><hi rend="italic">March</hi> 6,
                                1878</date>.<lb/>(Received March 6, 1878—10.30
                            a.m.)</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Preliminaries of peace between Turkey and Russia signed at San Stefano on
                            Sunday last.</p>
                        <closer><signed>MAYNARD</signed>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Pera.</hi></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>